324
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:59,400
对不起  我不能一个人养孩子
I'm sorry,but I can't raise a child on my own.

325
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:03,270
-那你不能告诉任何人 -好
-You don't tell anybody that I told you. -OK.

326
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:05,170
火药
Gunpowder.

327
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:07,830
填弹塞
Wadding.

328
00:29:09,610 --> 00:29:11,340
子弹
Then the bullet.

329
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:14,050
推弹杆
Ramrod.

330
00:29:18,690 --> 00:29:19,680
伸出你的手
Hold out your hand.

331
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:26,660
点燃火药时枪管并没有子弹
The bullet is not even in the gun when the charge is fired.

332
00:29:26,830 --> 00:29:30,460
知道了就没什么了不起
Once you know,it's actually very obvious.

333
00:29:31,670 --> 00:29:33,530
不过还是会...
