伸出另一只手
Hold out other hand.

602
00:50:18,980 --> 00:50:20,810
电流从哪里通过?
What's conducting the electricity?

603
00:50:20,990 --> 00:50:24,280
我们的身体能生产
Our bodies,Mr. Angier.

604
00:50:24,460 --> 00:50:26,950
并制造能源
Quite capable of conducting and,indeed,producing energy.

605
00:50:28,530 --> 00:50:30,550
你吃过了吗?
Have you eaten,Mr. Angier?

606
00:50:33,630 --> 00:50:35,620
