I can recognize an obsession.

627
00:51:40,970 --> 00:51:42,490
这不会有好事
No good will come of it.

628
00:51:42,670 --> 00:51:44,470
你自己着了魔也没好事吗?
Hasn't good come of your obsessions?

629
00:51:45,140 --> 00:51:47,730
一开始有  但我沉迷太久了
