00:59:47,330 --> 00:59:50,780
(全新移形遁影术)

747
00:59:51,700 --> 00:59:54,040
各位  你们今晚看到的
Ladies and gentlemen,much of what you've seen may be termed

748
00:59:54,210 --> 00:59:59,440
