I cannot claim this next feat as illusion.

751
01:00:09,720 --> 01:00:10,880
仔细看
Watch carefully.

752
01:00:12,360 --> 01:00:14,830
绝对看不到机关
You will see no trickery

753
01:00:15,300 --> 01:00:16,850
因为这是真的
for no trickery is employed.

754
01:00:18,030 --> 01:00:21,360
只有遥远东方的奇人异士
Merely a technique familiar to certain citizens of the Orient

755
01:00:21,530 --> 01:00:23,730
