01:04:43,800 --> 01:04:46,470
干我们这行  没有所谓的事实
Now that is a slippery notion

816
01:04:46,640 --> 01:04:47,940
不是吗?  温小姐
in our line of work,isn't it,Miss Wenscombe?

817
01:04:50,080 --> 01:04:52,640
