1208
01:36:03,270 --> 01:36:05,790
不错的小戏院  魔术界的新秀
good up-and-coming magician.

1209
01:36:05,970 --> 01:36:08,440
-你回来了 -见到你真好  约翰
-You're back.  -It's good to see you,John.

1210
01:36:09,370 --> 01:36:11,970
不错的排练场
Good rehearsal space.

1211
01:36:12,140 --> 01:36:14,770
瞎子助手  我喜欢
Blind stagehands,I like it.

1212
01:36:14,940 --> 01:36:17,380
你一向都很会耍宣传噱头
You always had a good eye for publicity.

1213
01:36:17,550 --> 01:36:18,910
我需要你的帮忙
I need your help,John.

1214
